videos.description: Clemson's Al-Amir Dawes has his pass picked off by M.J. Walker, who takes it the other way for the easy slam in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Walker steals and slams for Florida State) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Walker steals and slams for Florida State

videos.description: Al-Amir Dawes dishes ahead to John Newman III, who throws down a powerful two-handed dunk in traffic to bring Clemson within a point of Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Newman's ferocious jam gets Clemson fans on their feet) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Newman's ferocious jam gets Clemson fans on their feet

videos.description: John Newman III sheds a defender with a behind-the-back move and aggressively attacks the rim to give Clemson the lead over Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Newman's coast-to-coast layup puts Clemson ahead) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Newman's coast-to-coast layup puts Clemson ahead

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, M.J. Walker sends Tevin Mack to the floor with a mean crossover and knocks down the jump shot as the buzzer sounds.
